  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To test the hypothesis that a regimen of 200 mg oral mifepristone, with the option of home
      administration, followed by 800 μg buccal misoprostol 24 hours later for abortion through 70
      days LMP will be feasible and acceptable in Singapore.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
